{"tid":2052002,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國留學生參加美示威滋事被捕 坦言:「官方指使」為黨做出貢獻","createTime":"2020-06-05T07:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T09:06:14.000Z","uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f777f5053b822d8712e279c962f2971290b6b68","tid":2052002,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/415/5ed34628076b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F415%2F5ed34628076b6.png&h=87c60fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國非裔男子佛洛伊德之死撼動美國社會，但局勢演變漸趨複雜，在示威遊行活動中，不僅有人搶劫砸毀商家趁火打劫、白人至上主義的法西斯團體也趁亂散播仇恨言論。然而，在搶劫與暴亂的行列中，也開始出現「小粉紅」的身影，幾名中國留學生被捕後坦言，是受到「戰狼」的指示上街藉機煽動滋事。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，數日前便不斷有消息傳出，美國示威遊行中有中國人在場，像是有人在白宮外面操著中國普通話口音，大聲喊道：「快走！」，昨日更傳出，一名疑似中國留美學生在推特炫耀，自己搶劫商店所得到的DIOR、GUCCI等名牌包。他不但高喊「熱愛祖國和共產黨」，還揚言要「把美國變為第二個香港」。<br />\n<br />\n在推特自稱居住在華盛頓州西雅圖市的25歲中國留學生「袁宏睿」，2日在推特PO出自己洗劫商店得來的名牌精品照，大言不慚的說：「這是我在西雅圖搶的GUCCI包包，好看嗎？」 他還嗆網友：「反賊還說要到FBI舉報我，簡直笑死我了」，甚至大言不慚說：「美國人還欠我們中國很多帳沒還！幾個包包而已，美國人幹嘛那麼小器？」強調這是熱愛祖國的表現。儘管他本人疑似已發聲明否認該事，但仍在網路迅速擴散瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據《法廣》報導，除了袁宏睿，還有一名署名「一個脫離了高級趣味的人」的中國留學生，他也炫耀自己搶來的「戰利品」，還說「一場暴亂，讓本就不富裕的家庭多了兩個LV」，此外還有中國網友在推特指出，發生在洛杉磯的暴亂中，當地警方逮捕3名中國留學生，3人坦言是受到中國大使館官員指示，上街參加遊行並藉機煽動，為黨做出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/417/5ed92f238efc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F417%2F5ed92f238efc6.jpg&h=5457a372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名疑似中國留美學生在推特炫耀，搶劫美國商店的DIOR、GUCCI等名牌包。   圖：翻攝推特<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/417/5ed92f02d119a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F417%2F5ed92f02d119a.jpg&h=7aeeab77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名疑似中國留美學生在推特炫耀搶劫美國商店的行為，還高喊「熱愛祖國和共產黨」。   圖：翻攝推特<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-06-05/417207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-06-05%2F417207&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3bd065ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-06-05/417207</a>"},{"pid":"171d54b6d964cab55f28349a964dfa10db7b1972","tid":2052002,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78afd443f601d1db590418d081fb3032c544f603","tid":2052002,"uid":48193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:37:06.000Z","msg":"揾人幫手做野揾個有腦嘅真係好重要"},{"pid":"9bd40f92ab2642f8f4dab259ecff2e2b010754c7","tid":2052002,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e865d4d1d4e2462c7047565725fe664d1da39214","tid":2052002,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bd40f92ab2642f8f4dab259ecff2e2b010754c7","tid":2052002,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"no<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係加速主義者"},{"pid":"277bde3ba438debe97e0adbe3756fed8ead93084","tid":2052002,"uid":81505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78afd443f601d1db590418d081fb3032c544f603","tid":2052002,"uid":48193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:37:06.000Z","msg":"揾人幫手做野揾個有腦嘅真係好重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明知香港台灣出名舉報小粉紅<br />\n都夠膽po上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係以為識中文就一定係支那同胞"},{"pid":"54e7b4a9abc0703f6bc7074e4cfcec9ad62cf117","tid":2052002,"uid":56239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"口交部仲唔光速同佢割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0940cf2602d13eded2534474557a35e19606177","tid":2052002,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78afd443f601d1db590418d081fb3032c544f603","tid":2052002,"uid":48193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:37:06.000Z","msg":"揾人幫手做野揾個有腦嘅真係好重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"以為無腦容易控制<br />\n結果反手回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}